{"tid":1498532,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"羅傑斯相信港元匯價會持續下跌 最終與美元脫鈎","createTime":"2019-08-23T12:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T15:58:17.000Z","uid":47132,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fd8e123a4c45ba32b5b134f015a68d08db045480","tid":1498532,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T12:27:05.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 有「商品大王」之稱的羅傑斯(Jim Rogers)接受《今日俄羅斯》訪問時表示,受到反修例引起的連串示威抗爭活動影響,香港國際金融中心地位,已經搖搖欲墜,愈來愈多投資者,將資產轉移到新加坡等地避險。<br />\n<br />\n他稱,香港面對的資金外流情況,不是單純反映即時的危險,更顯示出未來香港市場將愈來愈不安全,而資金避走及沒有人來港投資,將會令到香港,作為主要金融中心的角色,逐漸褪色。<br />\n<br />\n羅傑斯指,另一項資金外逃的指標是港元。他相信港元匯價可能會持續下跌,令聯繫匯率難以維持,最終港元與美元脫鈎,甚至消失。<br />\n<br />\n他認為,若人民幣能取代港元,港元也會與美元脫鈎,但相信這只會在人民幣完全實現自由兌換時,才會發生。<br />\n<br />\n至於本港資金外流,羅傑斯認為,最大的得益者將會是新加坡,因當地人也說中文,投資也很方便,而且當地經濟也較穩定。 (BC)"},{"pid":"0912c6287d4ef5c51befe691b67161aaf37eceff","tid":1498532,"uid":58413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:38:29.000Z","msg":"即係無事"},{"pid":"fb73198e0f56784ddcb50859796ab904eb3dba98","tid":1498532,"uid":76591,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:42:35.000Z","msg":"呢條pk燈過燒山"},{"pid":"cc7f8f32f34893af1e1d04898d7eb186c5255c72","tid":1498532,"uid":198343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯既唔洗睇"},{"pid":"4f3ab607db14863d649fa9ab58387fde8bd24c54","tid":1498532,"uid":111811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb73198e0f56784ddcb50859796ab904eb3dba98","tid":1498532,"uid":76591,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:42:35.000Z","msg":"呢條pk燈過燒山"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f45a3e5c2dfef6bc49a6c091de21728ab064b62","tid":1498532,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:34:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fcall-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=5b828e90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n<br />\n全能既香港人連一份簽名都完成唔到？"},{"pid":"89807ea275add94f3b66da8e6de38abcc102438b","tid":1498532,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"變成小漁村<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27724551b839bc1b6c161ce74ae82c2226ba2e80","tid":1498532,"uid":46299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:58:17.000Z","msg":"「這只會在人民幣完全實現自由兌換時，才會發生。」<br />\n明晒"}]}